Can confirm that this issue seems to still appear - I'd second @achristensen56 and @serhannn in that noting when running graph definitions multiple times causes it to ragequit, and restarting Jupyter fixes it.

It's a corker of an error to run into as you end up questioning your own understanding of maths :p
